gw.api.web.disbursement

Class DisbursementDisplayDateRange

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.web.disbursement.DisbursementDisplayDateRange

  • public class DisbursementDisplayDateRange
extends java.lang.Object
    A DisbursementDisplayDateRange is one option in a dropdown selector shown in the UI on the Desktop Disbursements page. The dropdown selector lets the user filter the disbursement search results based on the age of the disbursement A DisbursementDateRange consists of a display key and an integer number of days.

    ccampo
